Package: Epicalculator
Type: Package
Title: Calculator for Analyzing Epidemiological Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sadia Sharmin, Catrina Mueller-Leonhard, Ze Zhang
Maintainer: <sadia_sharmin@brown.edu>
Description: This package was created to contain tools designed for epidemiological data analysis.    The functions are based on count data provided in traditional two-by-two tabular data format. They have the capability of analyzing stratified data and performing chi-square hypothesis testing of homogeneity. 
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
